headline: NRG Energy, Inc. Announces Dual Listing on NYSE Texas
summary: HOUSTON, August 18, 2025--NRG Energy, Inc. (NYSE:NRG) today announced the dual listing of its common stock on NYSE Texas, the newly launched, fully electronic, equities exchange headquartered in Dallas, Texas.
